<p>Oscar-nominated producer Chris Columbus (Harry Potter, Home Alone) directed and co-wrote the merry sequel with The Christmas Chronicles screenwriter Matt Lieberman.</p>

<p>Missing from the trailer was the sequel's villain - magical troublemaker Belsnickel - who's played by Deadpool 2 star Julian Dennison.</p>

<p>And while TCC2 features Judah Lewis, Kimberly Williams-Paisley, and Tyrese Gibson, Goldie's real-life son Oliver Hudson will not be back as deceased dad Doug Pierce in flashbacks.   </p>

